title: Zoya Anchor Base Coat .5 oz
description: Zoya Anchor Base Coat .5 oz ZOYA Anchor features a polymer technology that creates a microscopic anchor to powerfully fasten polish to the nail. ZOYA Anchor basecoat grips the nail plate and holds on color by forming a flexible bond between the nail plate and polish to dramatically extend polish wear. No more lifting, chipping or peeling. Contains an intense protein formulation to strengthen nails without causing brittleness. Directions: Remove existing polish, clean and prep nails with ZOYA Remove+ , apply one coat of ZOYA Anchor Basecoat or ZOYA Get Even Ridge Filling Basecoat , follow with two coats of ZOYA Professional Nail Lacquer , apply one coat of ZOYA Armor Topcoat/UV Block and add one drop of ZOYA Hurry Up Speed Dry to each nail. Formaldehyde, toluene, dibutyl phthalate and camphor free formula. .5 oz Also available as a part of the Zoya Color Lock System . Please, note: this item can be shipped to 48 contiguous United States via Ground Service only.
